                        325$ / Month
                    </p>
                    <a class="cardItem-detailBtn" href="/">
                        View Detail <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-3">
                <div class="cardItem" href="/">
                    <h3 class="cardItem-headingName">
                        SN299
                    </h3>
                    <img class="cardItem-thumbnail" src="~/Content/Images/demo.jpg" alt="Thumbnail" />
                    <p class="cardItem-price">
